2.  **Right-hand side (RHS):** `(concat1 ∘ List.map fromRA.frm) (consRA.consT (Tree.leaf x) (List.foldr consRA nilRA ((concat1 ∘ List.map fromRA.frm) (Digit.one t :: ds))))`
